g-purple-950/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-purple-800/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-md\"><span class=\"text-black font-bold text-sm\">K</span></div><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-lg hidden sm:block\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">kart.krd</span></div><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-200 animate-pulse\"></div></header><div class=\"pt-14\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#0f0520] text-white\" dir=\"rtl\"><header class=\"border-b border-purple-900/40 bg-[#0f0520]/80 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"bg-purple-900/30 border border-purple-700/50 rounded-lg p-1 flex\"><button class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium transition-all bg-yellow-400 text-black\">KU</button><button class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium transition-all text-purple-300 hover:text-white\">EN</button></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-black font-bold text-sm\">K</span></div><span class=\"font-bold text-xl text-white\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">kart.krd</span></div><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-amber-500 text-black font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm hover:from-yellow-300 hover:to-amber-400 transition-all\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\" href=\"/editor\">دروستی بکە</a></div></header><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-purple-700/20 rounded-full blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-amber-500/10 rounded-full blur-2xl\"></div></div><div class=\"relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pt-24 pb-20 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-block bg-purple-900/40 border border-purple-700/50 text-purple-300 text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-8\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">✦ بەخۆڕایی — بەبێ تۆمارکردن</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">کارتی بزنسی ئامادەکە<br/><span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-amber-500\">لە چەند چرکەیەکدا</span></h1><p class=\"text-purple-200 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">کارتی بزنسی پیشەیی بۆ خۆت ئامادەبکە — بەکوردی، عەرەبی، یان ئینگلیزی. پی‌دی‌ئێف دابەزێنە، بەبێ هیچ تۆمارکردنێک.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center\"><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-amber-500 text-black font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg hover:from-yellow-300 hover:to-amber-400 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/20 w-full sm:w-auto\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\" href=\"/editor\">🎨 دروستی بکە — بەخۆڕایی</a><span class=\"text-purple-400 text-sm\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">هیچ تۆمارکردنێک پێویست نییە</span></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-4\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">چوار شێوازی جیاواز</h2><p class=\"text-purple-300 text-center mb-12\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">شێوازێک هەڵبژێرە کە لە خۆت نوێنەرایەتی بکات</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><a href=\"/editor?template=modern\"><div class=\"group\"><div class=\"relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-900 to-purple-800 mb-3 border border-white/10 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"aspect-ratio:3.5/2\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-2 bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-400 to-amber-500\"></div><div class=\"pr-4\"><div class=\"w-24 h-3 bg-white/80 rounded mb-2\"></div><div class=\"w-16 h-2 bg-white/50 rounded\"></div></div><div class=\"pr-4\"><div class=\"w-20 h-2 bg-white/40 rounded mb-1\"></div><div class=\"w-24 h-2 bg-white/40 rounded\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">مۆدێرن</span><span class=\"text-purple-400 text-sm mr-2\">— <!-- -->Modern</span></div></div></a><a href=\"/editor?template=classic\"><div class=\"group\"><div class=\"relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 mb-3 border border-white/10 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"aspect-ratio:3.5/2\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between\"><div class=\"border-2 border-amber-500/60 inset-2 absolute rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"w-20 h-2.5 bg-gray-700/60 rounded mb-2\"></div><div class=\"w-14 h-2 bg-gray-500/50 rounded\"></div></div><div><div class=\"w-16 h-1.5 bg-gray-500/40 rounded mb-1\"></div><div class=\"w-20 h-1.5 bg-gray-500/40 rounded\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">کلاسیک</span><span class=\"text-purple-400 text-sm mr-2\">— <!-- -->Classic</span></div></div></a><a href=\"/editor?template=bold\"><div class=\"group\"><div class=\"relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-950 to-gray-900 mb-3 border border-white/10 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"aspect-ratio:3.5/2\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-yellow-400\"></div><div><div class=\"w-28 h-4 bg-white/90 rounded mb-2\"></div><div class=\"w-20 h-2.5 bg-yellow-400/80 rounded\"></div></div><div><div class=\"w-20 h-2 bg-white/40 rounded mb-1\"></div><div class=\"w-24 h-2 bg-white/40 rounded\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">بۆڵد</span><span class=\"text-purple-400 text-sm mr-2\">— <!-- -->Bold</span></div></div></a><a href=\"/editor?template=minimal\"><div class=\"group\"><div class=\"relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 mb-3 border border-white/10 hover:scale-105 cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"aspect-ratio:3.5/2\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"w-24 h-3 bg-gray-700/70 rounded mb-2\"></div><div class=\"w-16 h-2 bg-gray-500/50 rounded\"></div></div><div><div class=\"w-full h-px bg-gray-300/60 mb-2\"></div><div class=\"w-20 h-1.5 bg-gray-400/50 rounded mb-1\"></div><div class=\"w-24 h-1.5 bg-gray-400/50 rounded\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-medium\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">مینیمال</span><span class=\"text-purple-400 text-sm mr-2\">— <!-- -->Minimal</span></div></div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 border-t border-purple-900/30\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-800/30 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🌐</div><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">سێ زمان</h3><p class=\"text-purple-300 text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">کوردی، عەرەبی، ئینگلیزی — هەموو لەگەڵ پشتگیری چەپ‌بەراستەوە و ڕاست‌بەچەپەوە</p></div><div class=\"bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-800/30 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">⚡</div><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">خێرا و ئاسان</h3><p class=\"text-purple-300 text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">زانیاریت داخڵ بکە، پێشبینی زیندوو ببینە، PIF دابەزێنە — هەمووی لەسەر وێب</p></div><div class=\"bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-800/30 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🎨</div><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl mb-2\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">چوار شێواز</h3><p class=\"text-purple-300 text-sm leading-relaxed\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">مۆدێرن، کلاسیک، بۆڵد، مینیمال — شێوازێک هەڵبژێرە کە لە پیشەی خۆت نوێنەرایەتی بکات</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/60 to-indigo-900/60 border border-purple-700/40 rounded-3xl p-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">ئەمڕۆ کارتەکەت ئامادەبکە</h2><p class=\"text-purple-200 mb-8\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\">بەخۆڕایی — بەبێ تۆمارکردن — PIF دابەزێنە</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-amber-500 text-black font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg hover:from-yellow-300 hover:to-amber-400 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-amber-500/20\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Noto Sans Arabic&#x27;, sans-serif\" href=\"/editor\">دروستی بکە — ئیستا</a></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-purple-900/30 py-8 text-center text-purple-500 text-sm\"><p style=